<h1>Race / Hedging (Stable)</h1>
<p>Launch multiple providers simultaneously or with staggered delays; first successful completes.</p>
<pre><code>policy: {
  race: {
    contenders: [
      { model: 'gpt-4o', delayMs: 0 },
      { model: 'claude-3-haiku', delayMs: 120 }
    ],
    cancelOthers: true
  }
}
</code></pre>
<p>Reduces p99 latency at modest cost. Use for user-facing interactive flows.</p>
